Johnny Whitworth https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johnny_Whitworth 0 Johnny Whitworth (born October 31, 1975) is an American actor. Whitworth is best known for his performance as villain Blackout in the superhero film Ghost Rider: Spirit of Vengeance (2011). Johnny_Whitworth ( born October_31_,_1975 ) is an_American_actor .
